title: (Tues Full) Why Bobby Got Emotional Last Night + Amy’s Son Wants A YouTube Channel + Lunchbox Tries to Make Money Guessing Classic Country Songs
itunes:title: (Tues Full) Why Bobby Got Emotional Last Night + Amy’s Son Wants A YouTube Channel + Lunchbox Tries to Make Money Guessing Classic Country Songs
description:
Amy’s 11-year-old son came to her and said he wants to start a YouTube channel. She doesn’t know how she feels about him putting videos out on the internet. Lunchbox is back trying to guess the artists singing very famous classic country songs. This time he tries to win cash for each song he can get correct.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
